The '''''Millennium'' fighter''' was a [[Starfighter/Legends|starfighter]] designed chronologically after the ''[[Millennium Hawk]]'' by [[Millennium Astro-Engineering]]. It was larger and slower than its predecessor, but boasted a much heavier payload of firepower.

